        <item>
            <title>【有片睇】2023 Excel 世界电竞赛，澳洲数据分析专家倪安德蝉联</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/2023-excel-gaminig/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=2023-excel-gaminig</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/2023-excel-gaminig/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 11:53:02 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Excel]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电竞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1211021</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>相信很多朋友上班时都会用到 Excel，但你知道这款生产力软件也可以拿来「电竞」吗？2023 年 Excel 世界锦标赛由来自澳洲的数据分析专家倪安德再度蝉联夺冠，赢得 3000 美元（约港币 23,394.52 元）奖金。</p><p>今年 Excel 世界锦标赛（Microsoft Excel World Championship）刚刚在美国赌城拉斯维加斯圆满结束，这项比赛同一时间跨平于 Twitch、YouTube 及 ESPN 直播。今年冠军头衔及 3,000 美元奖金继续由去年冠军倪安德蝉联夺得。倪安德是来自澳洲的数据分析专家。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1211042" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-0-2-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-0-2-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-0-2-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-0-2-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-0-2-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-0-2-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1211041" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Las-128-Last-64-Rounds-1-19-15-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Las-128-Last-64-Rounds-1-19-15-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Las-128-Last-64-Rounds-1-19-15-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Las-128-Last-64-Rounds-1-19-15-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Las-128-Last-64-Rounds-1-19-15-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Las-128-Last-64-Rounds-1-19-15-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Excel 世界锦标赛每年都会假设一个案例，参赛者需要扭尽六壬使用 Excel 内的功能去解决这个「案例」，例如今年决赛的案例就有关穿梭机制作及行省采矿。比赛分为 3 部分，每部分 30 分钟。比赛是以用 Excel 技巧为中心，但仍然有不同的声光表演元素，让观众看得热血沸腾。今年比赛现场有 Excel 培训师 Jon Acampora 和 Oz du Soleil 作旁白讲解比赛。</p><p>今年比赛加入了新赛程，就是准决赛开始 7.5 分钟后将会淘汰得分最低的参赛者，而系统出现故障令裁判团误淘汰倪安德。过后裁判团开会商讨后将错误归咎于电脑故障，并重新邀请倪安德重新回归比赛。倪安德在比赛尾声完成了加分题，领先跟随其后的选手达 196 分，而倪安德本人更在比赛余下半分钟时除低耳机，直接两手一摊坐等胜利。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1211043" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-2-56-8-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-2-56-8-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-2-56-8-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-2-56-8-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-2-56-8-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Microsoft-Excel-World-Championship-2023-Finals-2-56-8-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>实际上 Excel 世界锦标赛已存在逾 10 年，不过去年 ESPN 才开始传播这项才赛事。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_86549"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UDGdPE_C9u8?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/3/23817220/excel-esports-espn-the-ocho-championship-start-time-watch">The Verge</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UDGdPE_C9u8">YouTube</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://hk.news.yahoo.com/excel%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7-%E7%AB%9F%E9%82%84%E6%9C%89-%E5%A0%B4-%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E6%AF%94%E8%B3%BD-excel%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%8C%A6%E6%A8%99%E8%B3%BD%E5%9C%A8%E6%AF%94%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC-042841666.html">数位时代</a>、<a href="https://www.wsj.com/tech/microsoft-world-excel-championships-las-vegas-448c5f0b">Wall Street Journal</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/18/2023-excel-gaminig/game-channel/">【有片睇】2023 Excel 世界电竞赛，澳洲数据分析专家倪安德蝉联</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
